marketing-text: Vula iqonga lomthombo ledatha yeCOVID19. Ideshibhodi eqhubela phambili ngesandisi sokongezwa kunye ne-API yamahhala eneenkcukacha, efumaneka kuzo zonke iilwimi.
name: Igama
promo-message: Yenziwe luthando ❤️ liqela kwiHoobu.com. Cwangcisa uhambo lwakho lwangemva kobhubhane ngoku kunye nesicwangciso sethu sobuchule sexesha lokusebenzisana
general-advice-wash-hands-description: Hlamba izandla rhoqo kunye nemizuzwana engama-20 usebenzisa isepha namanzi emva kokubetha impumlo yakho, ukhohlela okanye ukudumba nangaphambi kokuba utye okanye uphathe ukutya. Ukuhlamba izandla ngokufanelekileyo yeyona ndlela isebenzayo yokubulala intsholongwane.
general-advice-minimise-contact-descript: Cutha iintlanganiso ezingabalulekanga kunye nohambo kwaye ufune ezinye iindlela zokubulisa njengokuxhawula isandla, ukuqhawula okanye ukwanga.
general-advice-avoid-face-description: Izandla zinokuthatha ngokulula iintsholongwane kwaye ziye zangcoliseka, izandla zinokuyihambisa le ntsholongwane emehlweni akho, impumlo okanye umlomo. Ukusuka apho, intsholongwane inokungena emzimbeni wakho ikwenze ukuba ugule.
general-advice-be-hygienic-description: Ukumboza umlomo kunye neempumlo ngentonga egobile okanye ngezicubu zakho xa ukhohlela okanye uthimla, kwaye ulahla izicubu ezisetyenzisiweyo kwangoko.
general-advice-self-isolate-description: Ukuba ukhula njengomkhuhlane njengeempawu kufuneka uzimele wedwa njengenyathelo lokuthintela kwaye uphephe umngcipheko wokusasazeka kwesi sifo ngokuhlala ekhaya.
